FPS karakterinde instant-hit ates icin kameradan ileri yone line trace atabilirsin.

```cpp
#include "Camera/CameraComponent.h"
#include "DrawDebugHelpers.h"

void AMyProjectCharacter::FireLineTrace()
{
    if (!FirstPersonCameraComponent)
    {
        return;
    }

    const FVector Start = FirstPersonCameraComponent->GetComponentLocation();
    const FVector End = Start + FirstPersonCameraComponent->GetForwardVector() * 20000.0f;

    FHitResult Hit;
    FCollisionQueryParams Params;
    Params.AddIgnoredActor(this);

    const bool bHit = GetWorld()->LineTraceSingleByChannel(
        Hit,
        Start,
        End,
        ECC_Visibility,
        Params
    );

    const FVector TraceEnd = bHit ? Hit.ImpactPoint : End;
    DrawDebugLine(GetWorld(), Start, TraceEnd, FColor::Green, false, 2.0f, 0, 1.5f);

    if (bHit && Hit.GetActor())
    {
        UE_LOG(LogTemp, Log, TEXT("Hit: %s"), *Hit.GetActor()->GetName());
    }
}
```

Header tarafinda kamera icin `UPROPERTY(VisibleAnywhere) UCameraComponent* FirstPersonCameraComponent;` tutmak yaygindir.

Sweep, bir şekli iki nokta arasında hareket ettirip çarpışan aktörleri bulur. AoE, melee hitbox veya projectile yakın kontrolü için kullanılabilir.

```cpp
TArray<FHitResult> Hits;
FVector Start = GetActorLocation();
FVector End = Start + GetActorForwardVector() * 500.0f;
FCollisionShape Sphere = FCollisionShape::MakeSphere(75.0f);

bool bHit = GetWorld()->SweepMultiByChannel(
    Hits,
    Start,
    End,
    FQuat::Identity,
    ECC_Pawn,
    Sphere
);

if (bHit)
{
    for (const FHitResult& Hit : Hits)
    {
        AActor* HitActor = Hit.GetActor();
        if (HitActor)
        {
            UE_LOG(LogTemp, Log, TEXT("Sweep hit: %s"), *HitActor->GetName());
        }
    }
}
```

Debug için `DrawDebugSphere` veya `DrawDebugCapsule` eklemek çarpışma hacmini görmeyi kolaylaştırır.

